  "texts": [
    "We do not claim that our prompts were optimal for the task of writing the paper.",
    "Our prompts could also have introduced biases or preconceived notions, potentially influencing the content generated by the model.",
    "The absence of alternative prompts limits the understanding of GPT-4's performance in different contexts or writing tasks.",
    "Furthermore, the study did not explicitly assess GPT-4's interpretation of the prompts, which is crucial for comprehending its comprehension and ability to generate accurate responses.",
    "These limitations highlight the need for future research to employ varied prompts, ensure unbiased language, and assess prompt interpretation to provide a more comprehensive evaluation of GPT-4's capabilities."
